{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id1440b936-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"362"},"text":"§ 362.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Misbranded cosmetics","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"A cosmetic shall be deemed to be misbranded—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b937-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If its labeling is false or misleading in any particular.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b938-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If in package form unless it bears a label containing (1) the name and place of business of the manufacturer, packer, or distributor; (2) an accurate statement of the quantity of the contents in terms of weight, measure, or numerical count; and (3) the information required under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s364e"},"text":"section 364e of this title","children":[],"tail":": "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That under clause (2) of this paragraph reasonable variations shall be permitted, and exemptions as to small packages shall be established, by regulations prescribed by the Secretary."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b939-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If any word, statement, or other information required by or under authority of this chapter to appear on the label or labeling is not prominently placed thereon with such conspicuousness (as compared with other words, statements, designs, or devices, in the labeling) and in such terms as to render it likely to be read and understood by the ordinary individual under customary conditions of purchase and use.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b93a-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If its container is so made, formed, or filled as to be misleading.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b93b-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it is a color additive, unless its packaging and labeling are in conformity with such packaging and labeling requirements, applicable to such color additive, as may be contained in regulations issued under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s379e"},"text":"section 379e of this title","children":[],"tail":". This paragraph shall not apply to packages of color additives which, with respect to their use for cosmetics, are marketed and intended for use only in or on hair dyes (as defined in the last sentence of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s361/a"},"text":"section 361(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id1440b93c-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s362/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If its packaging or labeling is in violation of an applicable regulation issued pursuant to section 1472 or 1473 of title 15.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id1440b93d-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-25/ch675/s602"},"text":"June 25, 1938, ch. 675, § 602","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/52/1054"},"text":"52 Stat. 1054","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/86/618/tI/s102/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 86–618, title I, § 102(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1960-07-12"},"text":"July 12, 1960","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/74/398"},"text":"74 Stat. 398","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/601/s6/f"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–601, § 6(f)","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 7(f), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-30"},"text":"Dec. 30, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1673"},"text":"84 Stat. 1673","children":[],"tail":", renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tXII/s1205/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title XII, § 1205(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/716"},"text":"95 Stat. 716","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/571/tI/s107/12"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–571, title I, § 107(12)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-29"},"text":"Oct. 29, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/4499"},"text":"106 Stat. 4499","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/328/dFF/tIII/s3503/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–328, div. FF, title III, § 3503(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-29"},"text":"Dec. 29, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/5858"},"text":"136 Stat. 5858","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id1440b93e-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id1440b93f-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id1440b940-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsec. (b)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/328"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–328","children":[],"tail":" added par. (3) before proviso."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Par. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/571"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–571","children":[],"tail":" substituted “379e” for “376”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1970—Par. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/601"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–601","children":[],"tail":" added par. (f)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1960—Par. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/86/618"},"text":"Pub. L. 86–618","children":[],"tail":" added par. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id1440b941-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id1440b942-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":